{"tid":1910132,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國變相充公全國口罩後不久，德國亦宣佈禁止出口口罩","createTime":"2020-03-04T12:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T04:16:07.000Z","uid":202464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dbf1ae4a96a38c19a347d130754bdd0f03a3c705","tid":1910132,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T12:29:30.000Z","msg":"德國星期三（4日）早上亦傳來禁止口罩出口的消息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n禁令由衛生部和內政部聯合決定，有關法令已刊登在聯邦憲報，將由經濟部執行，即時生效。影響的物品較法國廣泛，除了口罩，手套、保護衣等醫護人員要在醫院工作時需要的保護物資，都禁止出口，唯一豁免是如果德國要參與國際援助，把有關物資贈送他國。<br />\n<br />\n另外，大部份治療地點的醫護人員保護物資，將由聯邦衛生部中央採購及分配。<br />\n<br />\n這個基本上跟法國的「徵用令」的精神一致&mdash;&mdash;物資「充公」，中央分配。法國沒列明禁止出口，但有關法令列明口罩生產線都要聽從國家指揮下，基本上可視作已禁止出口。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_8.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feuropechinese.blogspot.com%2F2020%2F03%2Fblog-post_8.html&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=e337c1e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://europechinese.blogspot.com/2020/03/blog-post_8.html</a>"},{"pid":"74a36451926b7c88b012860f5349e170e3840e96","tid":1910132,"uid":25183,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T12:37:11.000Z","msg":"日本同美國仲未禁<br />\n要被支那蝗爆買喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e05baa08a60597dee6bb60989271fc1759c583ef","tid":1910132,"uid":54262,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T12:57:55.000Z","msg":"其實日本點，仲好多亂傳"},{"pid":"12e95533bbd63f1d4e3de7a30764a59dea3a8974","tid":1910132,"uid":49445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T13:01:00.000Z","msg":"歐盟12噸防護裝備運中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更新時間 (HKT): 2020.02.03 02:20<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200203/6PWDABADEE65EVD24ZZ6DCJCSI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200203%2F6PWDABADEE65EVD24ZZ6DCJCSI%2F&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5